<Defs>

	<ThingDef ParentName="BiomesCore_CrabThingBase">
		<defName>BMT_RimCrab</defName>
		<label>rimcrab</label>
		<description>A mongrel crab species that can survive on most rimworlds in warm waters. It moves in large packs, which can be a threat to smaller islands because of their ravenous hunger. The animal’s hard shell makes it hard to get at it’s delicious meat, but the effort may well be worth it.</description>
